{"tid":1481923,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭自己仆緊街仲想陰d陰d送錢番大陸！！","createTime":"2019-08-18T02:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T10:13:53.000Z","uid":268358,"like":344,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":146,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe60de268727c375079dffec8373621f7b1d3ec","tid":1481923,"uid":268358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:13:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[/b]]林鄭想高價買大陸電！！[/b]</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">林鄭想用減少碳排放做理由，由環保角度入手，營造到香港需要向中國輸入可再生能源及核能！</span><br />\n<br />\n意咪住如果通過左又係 要不是有中國你們香港就玩蛋了.jpg 及極大量利益輸送！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，香港電商係可以解決到問題，而我地個賴死唔走的仆街第一樣就諗要賣港仲寫到好堂皇包裝到好撚靚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時，其實大陸電網自己都唔穩定！<br />\n睇睇this文 2017年霍建寧講的：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1724CaV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1724CaV.png&h=a98db173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條仆街有咩居心一目了然<br />\n<br />\n睇到e到，懇請大家幫幫手，唔好再比佢多條水喉，等支爆！<br />\n<br />\nFacebook路過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/au3rQrC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fau3rQrC.png&h=7442d1e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先要清楚知道佢設計到份問卷係好！撚！賤！<br />\n佢要引大家填到要支持佢最後目的：向中國高價買電！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n填寫時請明確記得佢目的！確保唔好比佢條題目fake到！！ </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">問卷連結在此：<a href=\"https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/vcf.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.susdev.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fvcf.php&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1EB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=86349048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/vcf.php</a></span><br />\n<br />\nFacebook 留言見有人post左sample<br />\n唔想暴露facebook所以無同答案的講聲就借左黎開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry<br />\n<br />\n問題三：<br />\n不⽀持 (更緊密的區域合作 &ndash; 包括向內地買電)<br />\n<br />\n問題五：<br />\n新建建築物：限制樓宇⾼度,避免加劇屏風效應<br />\n現有建築物：立法規定最⾼⼯時,港⼈減少超時⼯作,⾃然節省辦公場所⽤電<br />\n<br />\n問題六：<br />\n新建建築物：善⽤棕地,避免⼤規模填海建島⼯程<br />\n現有建築物：縮減內地來港單程證限額, 可減慢⼈⼝上升,住宅⽤電量增⻑亦將放緩<br />\n<br />\n問題九：<br />\n建議政府⾼官儘量採⽤步⾏、單⾞及公共交通⼯具,減少路⾯汽⾞流量,既環保,⼜可改善交通擠塞情況,更可深入認識基層市⺠需要<br />\n<br />\n問題⼗：<br />\n不同意輸入內地的可再⽣能源; 建議發展本地「分散式系統」（decentralized system）再⽣能源發電模式，在不同地點裝設規模較少的發電設施，發電後就地使⽤，有餘可輸送到電網。⽽根據理⼯⼤學的估計，單是在全港建築物天台加裝太陽能板，便可供應本地 6-10% 電⼒需求，這還未包括⽔塘、岩⽯坡、天橋上蓋等也可裝太陽能板的空間，可⾒我們應⽤太陽能的潛⼒亦⼗分優厚。(資料來源: 綠色和平)<br />\n<br />\n真係記得記得，唔好亂填！因為佢設計到份問卷係fake9你<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔處女post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,寫得1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都請大家幫幫手，推唔郁post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要補充資料請繼續補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝大家閱讀"},{"pid":"ba91d43eaf1cf7fe19c9c49e962ba833fefbb033","tid":1481923,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ae11911054304d94e76e029b7089ad09cb5d26","tid":1481923,"uid":268358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />p牌仔推唔郁post，請大家幫幫手！（其實係咪我開錯台？"},{"pid":"c0c62f43877772cd7fd9293d9cacae90c5bc1079","tid":1481923,"uid":16323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply